

@startuml
Start
:User asks to borrow a book;
if (Book available?) then (Yes)
   :Borrow a book;
   :Lend book to user;
   if (Successful?) then (Yes)
     :Show "Book successfully checked out" message;
   else (No)
     :Show message "Book could not be borrowed";
   endif
else (No)
   :Show "Book not available" message;
endif
Stop
@enduml